Element


action
&action.purpose;


&action.synopsis.gen;
Description



Actions are usually associated with GUIs.  An event might be movement or
clicking of the mouse, a change in focus, or any number of other
occurrences.


Processing expectations


&format.inline; &pexp.moreinfo;



&FutureChanges;


The content model of Action will be constrained to
(#PCDATA | Replaceable | InlineGraphic) in
DocBook V4.0.




&action.parents.gen;
&action.children.gen;

Attributes

moreinfo



If MoreInfo is set to RefEntry,
it implies that a RefEntry exists which further describes the
Action.





